<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent177ece5c1173458cb17da83e396fcc0c">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="North Downs Hospital, Surrey" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=117643"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>North Downs Hospital is one of the leading <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Private hospital in Surrey">private hospitals in surrey</a> with an excellent reputation for delivering high quality healthcare for self pay/insured and NHS patients. Located within the M25, close to the centre of Caterham, the hospital opened in 1974 and currently has 15 bedrooms, all with en suite facilities and a daycase suite.</p>
<p><strong>Opening Times</strong></p>
