<p><br/><br/>By investing in advanced medical technology, the hospital offers a wide range of <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/treatments" target="_blank" title="Healthcare treatments in Surrey">treatments</a>. Please click the <a href="/Services/hospitals/Services/DefaultView.aspx?id=203" target="_self">departments and services</a> for treatments available on Choose and Book.</p>
<p>The fully equipped ultra clean air theatre is particularly suitable for orthopaedic procedures offered such as arthroscopy, <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/treatments/orthopaedics" target="_blank" title="Orthopaedic Surgery in Surrey">hip and knee replacements</a>. The day unit is suitable for minor operations and endoscopy.</p>
<p>We have excellent levels of cleanliness and have effective infection control methods resulting in very low infection rates. All our facilities are regularly inspected and approved by the Care Quality Commission.</p>
<p>Free car parking and disabled access is also available.</p>
<p>Our consultants and nursing staff are highly experienced and have your care and comfort as their highest priority. During and after treatment, you will receive a standard of care which is second to none and all patients have the reassurance that theatre, paramedical services and a resident RMO is available 24 hours a day.</p>
<p>North Downs Hospital also provides private hospital treatments including full <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/treatments/diagnostic-services.aspx" target="_blank" title="Diagnostic Services">diagnostic</a> and endoscopy procedures, orthopaedic surgery, <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/treatments/physiotherapy" target="_blank" title="Physiotherapy in Surrey">physiotherapy,</a> <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/treatments/urology" target="_blank" title="Vasectomy in Surrey">vasectomy</a> and <a href="http://www.northdownshospital.co.uk/treatments/cosmetic-surgery" target="_blank" title="Cosmetic Surgery in Surrey">cosmetic surgery</a>.</p></div>
